   REPLACE DATDOK WITH MDATDOK
   REPLACE VALUTA WITH MVALUTA
   REPLACE BRNAL WITH MBRNAL
   REPLACE DOK WITH MDOK
   REPLACE DATUM WITH DATE()
   REPLACE VREME WITH TIME()   
   PDVU.GRD0.SETFOCUS
   PDVU.REFRESH 
   DO  FORM PDVUK 
ENDIF
